{"tid":918401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【越生越大】以為生痱滋原來係口腔癌 癌細胞更擴散至頸","createTime":"2018-11-27T07:43:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T13:57:55.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"af482172de23e659731333facf2a41632c350028","tid":918401,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T07:43:41.000Z","msg":"英國一名少女飽受舌頭長痱滋困擾，痱滋越長越大而且沒有好轉跡象，但醫生僅稱只是普通發炎，她也沒有加以理會。直至今年4月有牙醫發現她的痱滋長至比原本3倍大，始知道那並非痱滋而是口腔癌，要接受化療及放射性治療。<br />\n21歲來自唐克斯特市（Doncaster）的墨菲（Millie Murphy）稱：「我左邊舌頭有一粒痱滋，而我沒有想太多。有時我會碰到它，令我痛得晚上會坐著哭。」她曾經求醫，但醫生診斷後認為只是普通發炎。後來一段時間也未有好轉，再求醫時發現耳朵也發炎，最後才確診是口腔癌。<br />\n墨菲接受手術時，舌頭已有70%都被癌細胞侵蝕，癌症亦已擴散至舌底和頸部的淋巴結。她有時無法進食及說話，要接受喉管餵食，手術同時令她全身留下疤痕，「我的人生因為這件事而停頓，我要再次學習如何進食，也輕了25.4公斤（56磅）。」<br />\n8月時，墨菲的癌症已擴散至右頸，為免化療及放射性治療影響她的生育機會，她已冷凍儲存卵子留待日後使用，「口腔癌令人厭惡及難堪，我很擔心會因為患上這恐怖疾病而被人評頭品足。我只想這一切完結，可以重過新生活。」<br />\n墨菲表示假如外界對口腔癌有更多關注，她的情況應可及早發現並接受治療，故公開經歷希望提醒其他人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181126/large/1543221117_e101.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181126%2Flarge%2F1543221117_e101.jpg&h=d6aaea4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181126/large/1543221301_9300.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181126%2Flarge%2F1543221301_9300.jpg&h=f93dfa31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181127/58958734\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181127%2F58958734&d=LFry4mU5MBWBgVoBxpk3xQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=916ff787\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181127%2F58958734&h=8d5fc8fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181127/58958734</a>"},{"pid":"4722b22ffbed231ea4d24a594ea551eac74aebc4","tid":918401,"uid":36981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T07:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日生"},{"pid":"3403840c26bc79f96500164b1515250d15ee07b7","tid":918401,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T07:45:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54597077c263d096197501c738a001567d24ece4","tid":918401,"uid":48800,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T08:02:23.000Z","msg":"呢啲就一定有圖"},{"pid":"3852afd421a6c9da415267a5e4f2992d67ab0426","tid":918401,"uid":51435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T08:03:14.000Z","msg":"痛不欲生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c43def062ca800720136af7b74ce11d29957b9d","tid":918401,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54597077c263d096197501c738a001567d24ece4","tid":918401,"uid":48800,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T08:02:23.000Z","msg":"呢啲就一定有圖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T08:03:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e78e008f5cc05fe08329449a6a1c060ce232af0e","tid":918401,"uid":3037,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T08:03:43.000Z","msg":"上面張圖有打格下面嗰張冇 咁打格黎jm9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"939a747d9fc7a0a2182015ed2a0a0f56d493f82d","tid":918401,"uid":100347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T08:34:32.000Z","msg":"普通發炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e1df7fb